{"tid":866120,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[1月番補開] 新幹線變型機械人 Shinkalion","createTime":"2018-10-17T15:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:10:40.000Z","uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8e7100d554267074255474f44bee785017a275","tid":866120,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"播咗幾季都無人開 POST，唔知連登其實有無同好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/plarail/shinkalion/images/main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fplarail%2Fshinkalion%2Fimages%2Fmain.jpg&h=7ea5cd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於鐵道博物館地底的「新幹線超進化研究所」開發出了「新幹線變形機器人 Shinkalion」，對抗未知的巨大怪物體，能與 Shinkalion 高同步率的駕駛員，竟然是小學生們&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nJR 東日本同其他 JR 集團協力的大型企画，2018 年 1 月開始播放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n主角: 速杉ハヤト<br />\nCV: 佐倉綾音<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/hayato/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Fhayato%2Fimg.png&h=8e4104f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琦玉県大宮在住，Shinkalion E5 Hayabusa 駕駛員<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/e5/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2Fe5%2Fimg.png&h=caf5b287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男鹿アキタ<br />\nCV: 沼倉愛美<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/akita/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Fakita%2Fimg.png&h=ee4d6347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秋田県北秋田市出身，Shinkalion E6 Komachi 駕駛員<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/e6/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2Fe6%2Fimg.png&h=bd6b6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大門山 ツラヌキ<br />\nCV: 村川梨衣<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/tsuranuki/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Ftsuranuki%2Fimg.png&h=e173b553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石川県金沢市出身，自稱金沢土木王，Shinkalion E7 Komachi 駕駛員<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/e7/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2Fe7%2Fimg.png&h=26ce2c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n月山 シノブ<br />\nCV: 吉村那奈美<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/shinobu/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Fshinobu%2Fimg.png&h=c99efc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山形県米沢市出，Shinkalion E3 Tsubasa 駕駛員<br />\n(註: 這是男角)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/e3/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2Fe3%2Fimg.png&h=25c81767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清洲 リュウジ<br />\nCV: 逢坂良太<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/ryuji/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Fryuji%2Fimg.png&h=c9ecb620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛知県名古屋市在住，Shinkalion N700A Nozomi 及 Shinkalion Doctor Yellow 駕駛員<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/n700a/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2Fn700a%2Fimg.png&h=38e76053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n発音 ミク<br />\nCV: 藤田咲<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/miku/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Fmiku%2Fimg.png&h=bee57e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVOCALOID 初音 Collaboration，北海道札幌市出身，Shinkalion H5 Hayabusa 駕駛員<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/h5/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2Fh5%2Fimg.png&h=8dd9d2f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大空 レイ<br />\nCV: 松井恵理子<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/chara/rei/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fchara%2Frei%2Fimg.png&h=1463bb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北九州市出身，Shinkalion 800 Tsubame 駕駛員<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shinkalion.com/wp/wp-content/themes/shinkalion/image/anime/shinkarion/800/img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shinkalion.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2Fshinkalion%2Fimage%2Fanime%2Fshinkarion%2F800%2Fimg.png&h=4c6e554f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b251d610f9cbfb43f2afa2d1432013ee8dbd43d","tid":866120,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"仲有推介佐倉綾音超強嘅當地 P